channel.title: Flog It!
channel.desc: Antique experts Caroline Hawley and Nick Hall are on hand to find a selection of objects to take to auction. Caroline is delighted to find a painting by local artist Steven Dews, and Nick is bedazzled by some iconic seventies jewellery. Paul Martin visits the Wilberforce House Museum in Hull's Old Town to hear the amazing story of Hull-born William Wilberforce, the great anti-slave trade campaigner.
